      "rationale": "Relative errors are reported for pressure rise (3.2%), NIH (6.8% mean across 5 operating points), torque (4.5%), and velocity magnitude (8.0%). All values are within the defined acceptance thresholds. Comparisons include experimental uncertainty bands to contextualize agreement."
