    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level. Validation results demonstrate adequate agreement between CFD predictions and experimental measurements across the full COU operating envelope. The relative hemolysis index RH is below 1.0 for all five operating conditions, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The overall evidence package supports acceptance of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
